              "body": "`trust promote` writes PrevSHA from the current folded store state, but it never checks that this matches the pending entry’s OldSHA (the “SHA being replaced”). If the store changed between enqueue and promote (or the pending file is stale), this can record an incorrect prev_sha and violate the trust.jsonl schema contract. Consider requiring state[url].CurrentSHA to equal pending.OldSHA (or using pending.OldSHA as PrevSHA and failing if it conflicts).\n",
